| Location | ${safe(jobData.location)} |
| Fit Score | **${jobData.fit_score || 0}%** |
| ATS Score | ${jobData.ats_score || 0}% |
| Job Link | ${safe(jobData.job_url)} |

## Follow-Up Schedule
| Follow-up | Due Date | Status |
|-----------|----------|--------|
| Day 3 | ${safe(jobData.followup_day3)} | ⏳ Pending |
| Day 7 | ${safe(jobData.followup_day7)} | ⏳ Pending |
| Day 30 | ${safe(jobData.followup_day30)} | ⏳ Pending |
| Day 90 | ${safe(jobData.followup_day90)} | ⏳ Pending |

## Communication Log
| Date | Event | Status |
|------|-------|--------|
| ${safe(jobData.applied_date)} | Application submitted | ✅ Sent |

---

## 📄 Resume Analysis
${safe(jobData.resume_content)}

---

## 📄 Cover Letter
${safe(jobData.cover_letter_content)}

---

